<br>
I think everyone will agree there are 6 claimable camps (4 basements, 2 shrines).<br>
<br>
I have also seen people set up in the room above the basements quite frequently (no wanderers here btw).  So this is 4 more legitimate spots.<br>
<br>
If you are willing to kill wanderers occasionally (and there are like 4 of them?  6 max?  You can set up in dozens of places on the pathways, possibly with some good camps near the buildings with  2 or 3 humans in them that dot the zone.<br>
<br>
Although I wouldn't count it as a camp (being a pretty rude thing to do), there is quite often someone pulling to the graveyard.<br>
<br>
<br>
Also, talk to the druid/enchanter/whatever that is soloing in the basements.  They obviously are not holding all 18 spawns (or however many in those things).  I have made it a point to state, whenever I am soloing there and somebody does a camp check, that I am only claiming 3 or so spawns and people are welcome to take the rest. <p>Gatori Vonhinx<br>
