<br>
Because, ultimately, that's where it lies. You don't want the little folk to get in your way of the elemental planes, of RZ or your preperation of these things. But you can't keep us out of the zones. If we aren't allowed to kill the mobs people will quest to get access. <br>
<br>
Imo, AD is no different then BoT flag, PoNB, Trials, whatever.. just instead of 6 people, or 12 people, or 24 people, it flags 72 and should be treated as such. <br>
