The double standard being an alliance at whim, and of taking two shares of loot off rotation mobs, while needing to team mobs that drop even better loot, but insisting its just “flag progression”, and its all ok because “Hey, there’s a quest”.  Then do the quest. . .last I checked the quest didn’t drop Aerin Dar items, AND it prevents further progression to further gimping of the system by guilds teaming HoH trials or Mith Marr.<br>
