<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I would also point back to Emil’s listing of the loot off Aerin Dar, and repeat, that just because a guild bristling with Ssra weapons and VT gear finds those to not be much of an upgrade (and in some cases not an upgrade at all), doesn’t mean that guilds who have never even seen Arch Lich, High Priest, or Creator are going to find his drops anything less than amazing.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
